        "text": "this Office with a copy of a letter addressed to the Daily Oklahoman and\nTimes, Oklahoma City, Oklahoma, dated July 10, 1950. Copies of this letter\nwere designated for the FBI, Washington, and the Oklahoma City Police\nDepartment. The letter itself is quoted:"
      },
